  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1215">
<l>naṉaviṉāṟ kaṇṭatūu māṅkē kaṉavuntāṉ </l>
<l> kaṇṭa poḻutē yiṉitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw him in my waking hours, and then it was pleasant; I see him just now in my dream, and it is (equally) pleasant.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
